                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-anthony-tao" title="Posts by Anthony Tao" rel="author">Anthony Tao</a></span> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-31" pubdate>January 31, 2013 5:32 pm</time> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2013/01/china-rises-one-spot-in-latest-rsf-press-freedom-index/#comments">2</a></p>
						
