					    <article id="post-9626" class="post-9626 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-culture category-by-james-tiscione tag-gangnam-style tag-spring-festival clearfix" role="article">
						
						    <header class="article-header">
							
							    <h3 class="h2"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/2013/01/psy-lands-in-shanghai-celine-dion-tabbed-for-cctv-spring-festival-gala/" rel="bookmark" title="PSY Lands In Shanghai, Celine Dion Tabbed For CCTV Spring Festival Gala">PSY Lands In Shanghai, Celine Dion Tabbed For CCTV Spring Festival Gala</a></h3>
                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-james-tiscione" title="Posts by James Tiscione" rel="author">James Tiscione</a></span> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-30" pubdate>January 30, 2013 11:44 pm</time> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2013/01/psy-lands-in-shanghai-celine-dion-tabbed-for-cctv-spring-festival-gala/#comments">6</a></p>
						
						    </header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						    <section class="entry-content clearfix">
                                                        <div style="float: left;">
                                                                <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2013/01/psy-lands-in-shanghai-celine-dion-tabbed-for-cctv-spring-festival-gala/"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://beijingcream.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/PSY-and-Celine-Dion-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="PSY and Celine Dion" /></a>
                                                        </div>
                                                        Hunan will be spared a visit from Uncle PSY this Spring Festival, as it looks like he’ll be galloping on Dragon TV’s Spring Festival crap-a-thon in Shanghai, effectively making the Changsha government look like a bunch of liars.<!--
